profile:
Started in 2018, We Paint Ontario is a fresh face in the painting world.  We're a family oriented company that believes in customer satisfaction.  We take pride in our work and enjoy seeing customers and receiving feedback upon completion.

I, Aaron Bibok have several years in construction a lot of which has been spent in the painting industry.  

Our secretary, Victoria White has spent a majority of her career in accounting and dealing with the public.  She's our acting human resources representative and would be more than willing to help in any way at any time.
